prompts.prompt: I need a code to create a one-page website for selling enemas. The website should include all the features mentioned: a compelling headline, engaging product images, a clear and concise product description, benefits and uses section, customer testimonials and reviews, trust signals, clear pricing and shipping information, an FAQ section, a strong call-to-action, an easy checkout process, mobile optimization, SEO optimization, live chat or contact information, a privacy policy and terms of service section, and a secure payment gateway.
